milestones.description: Sese Bau and Lega Siaka's 110-run partnership is PNG's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 79 between Vani Morea and Lega Siaka
Airee and Dev Khanal's 129-run partnership is NEP's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 89 between Malla and Rohit Paudel
Sese Bau and Lega Siaka's 110-run partnership is PNG's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 98 between Sese Bau and Mahuru Dai
Airee and Dev Khanal's 129-run partnership is NEP's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 104 between Rohit Paudel and Aarif Sheikh
